Sentencas: The chemical reactivity of current collector pastes, utilized in electrode performance measurements, were investigated with respect to the solid oxide fuel cell composite cathode, (La85Sr15)(98)MnO3/8 mol% Y2O3-stabilized ZrO2 (LSM/YSZ).
Titulo: Chemical degradation of La1-xSrMnO3/Y2O3-stabilized ZrO2 composite cathodes in the presence of current collector pastes

Sentencas: Anode substrate single cells were prepared with Pt or Ag paste current collectors applied to the electrodes.
Titulo: Chemical degradation of La1-xSrMnO3/Y2O3-stabilized ZrO2 composite cathodes in the presence of current collector pastes

Sentencas: Phase purity of the cathodes before and after sintering the current collectors were examined with powder X-ray diffraction (XRD) and the performance of the cells determined with current-potential measurements.
Titulo: Chemical degradation of La1-xSrMnO3/Y2O3-stabilized ZrO2 composite cathodes in the presence of current collector pastes

Sentencas: XRD experiments provided evidence that Pt paste, containing a bismuth flux, reacted with the composite cathode at temperatures above 800 degreesC leading to formation of the pyrochlore phase, La2Zr2O7.
Titulo: Chemical degradation of La1-xSrMnO3/Y2O3-stabilized ZrO2 composite cathodes in the presence of current collector pastes

Sentencas: Cathodes coated with Ag paste, which did not contain a bismuth flux, showed no sign of chemical degradation.
Titulo: Chemical degradation of La1-xSrMnO3/Y2O3-stabilized ZrO2 composite cathodes in the presence of current collector pastes

Sentencas: Synthesized Bi-subnitrate and commercial Bi2O3 were shown to have similar chemical reactions with LSM/YSZ powders leading to pyrochlore phase formation.
Titulo: Chemical degradation of La1-xSrMnO3/Y2O3-stabilized ZrO2 composite cathodes in the presence of current collector pastes

Sentencas: Current-potential experiments on single test cells demonstrated that samples prepared with paste containing bismuth flux had a decrease in initial performance.
Titulo: Chemical degradation of La1-xSrMnO3/Y2O3-stabilized ZrO2 composite cathodes in the presence of current collector pastes
